quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  6,82,It is those who believe and confound not their belief with wrong doing. These! theirs is the security and they are the guided
  6,83,"And this was Our argument which We vouchsafed unto Ibrahim against his people. We raise in degrees whomsoever We list; verily thy Lord is Wise, Knowing"
  6,84,"And We bestowed upon him Is-haq and Ya'qub: each one We guided. And Nuh We had guided afore, and of his progeny Da-ud and Sulaiman and Ayyub and Yusuf and Musa and Harun. And thus We recompense the well-doers"
  6,85,"And also Zakariyya and Yahya and Isa and llyas: each one was of the righteous"
  6,86,"And Ismai'l and Alyas'a and Yunus and Lut: each one of them We preferred above the worlds"
  6,87,"And also some of their fathers and their progeny and their brethren: We chose them and guided them onto the right path"
  6,88,"This is the guidance of Allah whereby He guideth whomsoever of His bondmen He listeth. And if they had associated, to naught would have come all that they were wont to work"
  6,89,"Those are they unto whom We vouchsafed the Book and judgement and prophethood. Wherefore if those disbelieve therein, We have surely entrusted its unto a people who are not disbelievers therein"
  6,90,"Those are they whom Allah had guided, so follow thou their guidance, Say thou: no hire I ask therefor; it is but an admonition unto the worlds"